  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in the donabe vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped green onions and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add the pork or vegetable broth, soy sauce, and salt, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and add the ramen noodles, cooking for 3 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped shungiku and cook until wilted.",
    "Stir in the confit tomato.",
    "Serve the ramen hot, garnished with additional green onions if desired.",
    "Let the dish rest for a few minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld."
